ipt_ACCT is an accounting module for iptables.

a) [For 2.4 kernels]
  # make OLD_KERNEL=1
  # make OLD_KERNEL=1 install
b) [For 2.6 kernels]
  # make
  # make install

Additional parameters:
  PREFIX - Installation prefix (defaults to /usr/local) for headers and
           userland utilities.
  IPTABLES - Path to iptables binary (defaults to /sbin/iptables).
  IPTABLES_LIBS - Path to iptables shared libraries (defaults to /lib/iptables)
  MODULES_DIR - Path to kernel modules (defaults to /lib/modules/`uname -r`)
  KERNEL_SOURCES - Path to kernel sources (defaults to $(MODULES_DIR)/build)
  CC - C compiler (defaults to gcc)
  CFLAGS - C compiler flags (defaults to -O2)
  LD - GNU ld (defaults to ld) 

